            "initials": "KM",
            "avatar_color": "#f7d04e",
            "rating": 5,
            "headline": "I Thought My Metabolism Was Gone For Good",
            "text": "For years I felt like my body was working against me. I was eating reasonably well, staying active, and still watching the scale slowly creep up. The hardest part was feeling tired all the time and constantly thinking about food. Since adding Metabolic Flow to my routine, I feel more balanced, my cravings are much easier to manage, and I finally feel optimistic again. I only wish I had found it sooner."
          }
        },
        "review_4nE9ti": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Joanne Peters",
            "initials": "JP",
            "avatar_color": "#f7d04e",
            "rating": 5,
            "headline": "The Weight Kept Coming No Matter What I Tried",
            "text": "Once I hit my 50s, it felt like every pound was harder to lose than the last. I tried cutting carbs, intermittent fasting, and even working out more, but nothing seemed to make a difference. Metabolic Flow has helped me feel more in control of my habits, my clothes fit more comfortably, and I have so much more confidence than I did a few months ago."
          }
        },
        "review_e6ccYx": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Rebecca Johnstone",
            "initials": "RJ",
            "avatar_color": "#f3d2c2",
            "rating": 5,
            "headline": "My Favorite Jeans Fit Again",
            "text": "I wasn't looking for a miracle. I just wanted to feel comfortable in my clothes again. After a few weeks of taking Metabolic Flow, I started noticing small changes that really added up. I feel less driven by cravings, I have more energy throughout the day, and for the first time in years, I don't dread trying on my favorite jeans."
          }
        },
        "review_xyRQLk": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Michelle Harlow",
            "initials": "MH",
            "avatar_color": "#bcd3ef",
            "rating": 5,
            "headline": "I Finally Broke The Cycle Of Starting Over",
            "text": "Every Monday I promised myself I would get back on track, and every Friday I felt I had failed again. It was exhausting. Metabolic Flow has become one of the easiest parts of my routine. I feel more motivated, more consistent, and much more confident in my ability to stick with healthy habits long term."
          }
        },
