            "headline": "Friends Started Asking What I Was Doing",
            "text": "The funny thing is I didn't notice the changes right away. But friends and family started commenting that I looked happier and more energized. My afternoon crashes aren't nearly as bad as they used to be, I'm not constantly reaching for snacks, and I feel more like myself than I have in years."
